metadata.name: Dante - Circles of hell
metadata.description:
After more than 700 years, Dante and his circles of hell is back to our modern world. 

Renaissance and Cyberpunk in one piece of art, the past meeting the future.

The circles of hell represent the seven deadly sins, it is part of the "Divine Comedy" by Dante : a poem, a personal tale of redemption, a treaty on human virtue, as well as one of the most influential pieces of science fiction.


This is the first piece of the Cyberpunk Renaissance collection.
